Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.91,0:22:44.99,ED2J,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be2\fad(200,200)}嵐の後
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.20,0:22:48.02,ED2J,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be2\fad(200,200)}透き通る
