Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.33,0:22:31.65,ED2C,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be2\fad(200,200)}啊  瞬间风速
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.11,0:22:38.32,ED2C,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be2\fad(200,200)}被旋风扰动心神
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.52,0:22:41.50,ED2C,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be2\fad(200,200)}越上云端
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.91,0:22:44.99,ED2C,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be2\fad(200,200)}暴风雨之后
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.20,0:22:48.02,ED2C,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be2\fad(200,200)}清澈而明净
